Name: Celery
Description: Crisp and refreshing, it has little inherent taste on its own.

DescriptionLocalization.es: Crujiente y refrescante, tiene un pequeño sabor a sí mismo.
DescriptionLocalization.ko: 아삭아삭하고 신선한 셀러리는, 그 자체로는 맛이 거의 없습니다.
DescriptionLocalization.de: Knackig und erfrischend, hat wenig Eigengeschmack.
DescriptionLocalization.fr: Croustillant et rafraîchissant, son goût inhérent est faible.
DescriptionLocalization.hu: Ropogós és frissítő, de az íze magában semleges.
DescriptionLocalization.ja: 清々しく爽やかでいて、少し独特な味わい。
DescriptionLocalization.pt: Crocante e refrescante, possui um sabor especial.
DescriptionLocalization.ru: Хрустящий и освежающий, сам по себе практически безвкусный.
DescriptionLocalization.zh: 清爽提神，本身就没有什么内在的味道。
